rows.label: qst200413_msg0001
rows.name:
I have captured all the criminals
related to this case...

rows.label: qst200413_msg0002
rows.name:
Now that woman will no longer
be troubled by her debt.

rows.label: qst200413_msg0003
rows.name:
A job very well done, Vasara...
But next time, please do not
go off on your own.

rows.label: qst200413_msg0004
rows.name: ...I will see what I can do.

rows.label: qst200413_msg0005
rows.name:
Vasara, do you realize that
your selfish actions could
also endanger your comrades?

rows.label: qst200413_msg0006
rows.name:
And yet, there are times when
acting alone prevents danger
from befalling my comrades...

rows.label: qst200413_msg0007
rows.name: Now, now, let's put that aside for now.

rows.label: qst200413_msg0008
rows.name:
More importantly, we need to
tell Ellenora-san about this.

rows.label: qst200413_msg0009
rows.name:
You're right. Let's go and
put her mind at ease.
